Package: ggsegArslan
Title: Arslan Atlas for the 'ggseg' Ecosystem
Version: 2.0.0
Authors@R: c(person("Athanasia Mo", "Mowinckel",
                    email = "a.m.mowinckel@psykologi.uio.no",
                    role = c("aut", "cre"),
                    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5756-0223")))
Description: Arslan multi-level parcellation atlas for the 'ggseg' ecosystem.
    Provides a unified 'ggseg_atlas' object with both 2D polygon geometry and
    3D vertex indices, for use with 'ggseg' and 'ggseg3d'.
